headline: Trimble to Present at Piper Sandler Growth Frontiers Conference
summary: Trimble® (Nasdaq: TRMB) announced today that its Chief Financial Officer, Phil Sawarynski, will be presenting at the Piper Sandler Growth Frontiers Conference on Thursday, September 11, 2025 at 10:30am Central Time at the Virgin Hotel in Nashville, Tennessee.

headline: Farming as a Service Market Research 2025-2030 | Explore the Impacts of IoT, AI, 5G, and Autonomous Farming Drive Precision, Sustainability, and Agritech Startup Growth
summary: The global Farming as a Service (FaaS) market is projected to grow from US$4.70 billion in 2024 to US$11.78 billion by 2030, driven by increasing food demand and technological advancements. This innovative model offers farmers essential services such as precision farming tools, equipment rental, and access to markets on a subscription or pay-per-use basis.
